  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_020_000135",
    "sentence": "將之任所，寢疾，逾旬卒於河中。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_020_000136",
    "sentence": "太祖聞之，痛惜移晷。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_020_000137",
    "sentence": "開平初，追贈太保。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_020_000138",
    "sentence": "乾化三年，又追贈太傅。",
